preference.name: AWS_SearchPreFilter_Property1
preference.preference_description: Contains the required information needed to display the first PreFilter in the AWS client. The first value should be the type name and property name in the format: type.property e.g. POM_application_object.owning_user The second value onwards will be the internal values for the property e.g. infodba
